These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, november
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, trike
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Birthday   | august  | november |
| Transport     | trike | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bluemaster
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Cigar   | davidoff | bluemaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
2 different pets are kept: goat, mouse
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk   |
| Pet       | mouse  | goat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, purple
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, parkour
1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Color   | red  | purple |
| Sport         | cycling | parkour    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, thai
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, horror
1. the dutch is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Nationality      | dutch | thai |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | crime  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-6::.
